No. 10-329. Orjiakor Isiogu, et al., Petitioners v. Michigan Bell Telephone Company, dba AT&T Michigan. 562 U.S. 1198, 131 S. Ct. 1062,

178 L. Ed. 2d 862,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 1049. January 24, 2011.
